    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It's the perfect daily driver that still looks great pulling into any parking lot! I've made sure to keep up with all the maintenance, so it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with you. Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
